cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the optimization of handoff decision and load balancing in wireless networks, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT). The proposed algorithm also involves the use of Continuous Time Markov Chain (CTMC) Model, which is commonly used in system modeling and analysis (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the wastage of electrical energy in femto BSs, which can be considered as a topic related to multimedia systems (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) as it involves the protection of network resources.
